  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>For business or for leisure, Novotel Bangkok Platinum is an oasis of luxury &amp; comfort.  Located in the heart of Bangkok?s shopping district, Novotel Bangkok Platinum offers unrivaled contemporary accommodation. Situated above the renowned Platinum Fashion Mall, the hotel is minutes walk from Central World Shopping Mall, Pantip Plaza and Pratunam Market.  Spacious, contemporary in design, and adaptable, the Novotel Next Room is truly a place for living and perfect for all your needs.  The hotel consists of 283 bedrooms (including 11 suites and a dedicated Premier Floor), The Square Restaurant, Lobby Bar, meeting rooms and contemporary pool &amp; fitness facilities.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Located on the top of Platinum Fashion Mall, next to Central World, short walk to BTS stations Chidlom and Siam; 10 minutes walk from Siam square and Siam Paragon. 5 minutes by car to Airport express link station, direct access to the highway exit.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>Located on the Top of Platinum Fashion Mall, the hotel lobby is one the 6th floor. All glass building, oval shapes, very bright with floor to ceiling windows.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The Square Restaurant: The Square restaurant offers a trendy and chilled out dining venue with a large selection of International, Asian and Thai favorites; served with an extensive wine list.  Sunday is a special occasion for a brunch, full of gourmet delights including abundant seafood, cheeses and decadent desserts. Daily buffets and "A la carte" selection; breakfast buffet.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The hotel lobby is located on the 6th floor with direct access to Platinum Fashion Mall, high ceiling with the meeting rooms / ballroom on the mezzanine floor ( 7th). Platinum lounge ( lobby bar) benefits of a fantastic view looking at ratchaprasong and petchaburi intersection. The Square restaurant is connected to the lobby.</Text>
  </Description>
